title: Demi’s First Interview Since Coming Out on ‘Paradise’
description:
Demi Burnett opens up about speaking her truth and being part of Bachelor Nation’s first same-sex relationship. Plus, Nicole Lopez on the Jordan/ Christian fight and her experience in “Paradise.”
